0%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone provided an excellent, comprehensive service when drawing up my will and Lasting Power Attorney. Emily Owston was professional and answered all of my questions.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Moonstone Advocates. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I find this practice gives clients individual attention as needed. I can only speak for myself, but they have given me everything I asked for and advice when they felt it was needed. They have made me feel that they understand my problems and give me advice on how to deal with them.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Members of the team we have met are professional, friendly and knowledgeable, giving a tailor-made personal service making suggestions that are unique to our requirements.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Each member of the team I have come into contact with has been lovely &amp; they often go that extra mile to get the job done with the least inconvenience to myself &amp; other family members. They show care, sensitivity &amp; are very supportive. Nothing seems to be too much trouble.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very personal service, made to feel comfortable and supported. The confidence we felt in the advice given was second to none. Everything is explained at every step of the process.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families, and professionals across Uganda.</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I have been with Moonstone Advocates for many years and have nothing but praise for them. Without exception whoever has dealt with our legal issues &amp; requirements has been professional &amp; efficient, as well as sensitive &amp; supportive.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Private Wealth &amp; Succession Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section class=\"section_crosslink\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"crosslink_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid crosslink_content\"><div class=\"crosslink_content-left\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Other related services</h2></div><div class=\"w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"crosslink_item-list w-dyn-items\"><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"crosslink_item w-dyn-item\"><a list-link=\"trigger\" href=\"/leasehold-enfranchisement-management\" class=\"button is-text-link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"crosslink_item-text-wrapper\"><p>Leasehold Enfranchisement &amp; Management</p></div><div list-link=\"target\" class=\"crosslink_item-icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xxsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M676.2-445.93H188.09q-14.68 0-24.37-9.7-9.7-9.7-9.7-24.37 0-14.67 9.7-24.37 9.69-9.7 24.37-9.7H676.2L456.13-734.13q-10.2-10.2-10.33-24.03-.14-13.84 10.07-24.09 10.22-10.29 24.09-10.17 13.87.12 24.15 10.31l278 278q5.46 5.52 7.94 11.48 2.49 5.97 2.49 12.66t-2.49 12.63q-2.48 5.95-7.94 11.45l-278.24 278q-10.55 10.43-24